			<p>
			Additionally, a septe Pllel View window can be selected from the right click menu with <guimenuitem>Detach/Attach</guimenuitem>.
			Your Bible pane will return to its normal single text view, and the new Pllel View window will show the complete
			chapter, showing the same translations.
